snippet.title: Mario Kart Tour - Winter Tour Trailer
snippet.description:
【Mario Kart Tour】
Free-to-start, optional in-game purchases available. Persistent internet, compatible smartphone and Nintendo Account required. Data charges may apply.

App Store: https://apps.apple.com/app/id1293634699
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.nintendo.zaka

Follow along for an app introduction and the latest information.
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mariokarttourEN
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mariokarttour

For more information, visit the official website for detail.
https://mariokarttour.com

ESRB Rating: EVERYONE with In-game Purchases

Rated PEGI 3 (Digital Purchases)

USK ab 0 Jahren (Onlinekäufe)
